<section id="blog-post-2" class="level1">
<h1>Blog Post 2:</h1>
<p>I want to use maps to view data on different arrest statistics across the US from the “usdata” dataset. I’ll create 2 visualizations, 1 mapping murders/100k people and the other mapping assaults/100k people. I am curious as to what geo-spatial patterns may exist, if any. Next, I will pick another variable to map to try and explain one factor that could lead to high crime rates. I hope to use mapping to best show the trends in these data.</p>
