<section id="plot-3-exploring-possible-explantions-using-usdata-package." class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="plot-3-exploring-possible-explantions-using-usdata-package.">Plot 3: Exploring possible explantions using “usdata” package.</h2>
